{"tid":1679538,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何韻詩盼港人堅持： 那一線光正出現","createTime":"2019-10-28T09:08:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T11:02:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e2587421b62aa65c4b7bfad27175dfb0c297d673","tid":1679538,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T09:08:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20191028/20795085\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191028%2F20795085&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD5yfW%2F3rzywXjCQwsEwiLy3M%3D&h=dfcd8c77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191028%2F20795085&h=3b2710f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20191028/20795085</a><br />\n<br />\n何韻詩盼港人堅持：<br />\n那一線光正出現<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191028/large/1572183494_0c00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191028%2Flarge%2F1572183494_0c00.jpg&h=751dbb08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何韻詩在奧斯陸自由論壇演講，將香港人抗爭的聲音帶到世界。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191028/large/1572183496_a2c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191028%2Flarge%2F1572183496_a2c9.jpg&h=ae378749&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何韻詩（左）自言從沒想過抗爭也可以不孤單，還認識了許多世界各地的勇者。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n何韻詩由反送中運動開始，一直和爭取民主自由的港人站在一起，並多次到海外進行演講，上周三她在紐約出席了奧斯陸自由論壇，完成了海外最後一場演講後，前晚在社交網上報平安：「回家了。」她又紀錄了這場運動發展至今的一點感受，表示今年5月在運動爆發前，到奧斯陸參加首次演講，當時還在回顧2014年的成與敗，誰想到兩星期不到，香港人都回來了，還打了最漂亮一仗，直到此刻。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n得到更大能量<br />\n<br />\n何韻詩說：「我們都太習慣放大和只看到自己的困難，但原來在我們認知以外，有許許多多為不盡相同的原因，但又如此近似的理念而奮鬥的人。有些為保衞家園付上不能回家的代價，有些因為對抗極權，從此不能與親人相見。相比之下，我所經歷的如此微不足道。聽到他們的故事，也令人不禁更謙卑了，同時也令自己更有勇氣大步走下去。」她自言從沒想過抗爭也可以不孤單，還認識了許多世界各地的勇者，在不同人身上得到更大的能量和想法，但接下來要怎麼做？重點是怎樣再加強連結。<br />\n<br />\n要打敗極權，何韻詩提到不能單靠個人力量，惟有和想法相近的人，真正不分你我連成一線，才能創造更大的力量。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191028/large/1572183494_46f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191028%2Flarge%2F1572183494_46f6.jpg&h=5ddeb4fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何韻詩提到警察濫權的行為。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191028/large/1572183495_467f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191028%2Flarge%2F1572183495_467f.jpg&h=b047cb8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港眾志常委羅冠聰現身支持何韻詩。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n走到新交叉點<br />\n<br />\n何韻詩說：「做完這次演講，不知從何而來的直覺，有感又是另一個終點和起點的交滙點。有些甚麼又正在改變，在整體抗爭中又走到一個新的交叉點，有些想法和做法又是時候再upgrade了，不知對大家有沒有同感，起碼對於我個人來說是這麼想。至於那是甚麼，可能要多一點點時間來沉澱思考一下。」<br />\n<br />\n何韻詩之後再補充，表示：「我到此刻對於我們的抗爭仍然是正面和抱有希望的。香港人，請相信，我們正在改變世界。再多堅持一下，那一線光，正在出現。」<br />\n<br />\n撰文：葉晴 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n阿倫獲表揚小春冇份<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n【馮仁昭四圍超】SG感動送Jessica出嫁"},{"pid":"978e334ac1567bab70fd7c1f93770dc6a7a92fde","tid":1679538,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T09:08:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qXEs9qi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqXEs9qi.jpg&h=02cd3311&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"705b92d3973bfd9329d60fc7923ed54d20431699","tid":1679538,"uid":231480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T09:16:25.000Z","msg":"HOCC同羅冠聰，G鋒，同大專團隊好勁，外交官"},{"pid":"ae791323a7345c02fb79ec1c8d5659ddb762ec88","tid":1679538,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T09:27:24.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86845c4cfb7aa22d70368ab1e6738ae0dd542377","tid":1679538,"uid":281189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T09:30:15.000Z","msg":"犀利<br />\n你哋係會被驕傲地寫入香港歷史的一頁㗎<br />\n香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cec81290640cd1282970b0946f228a519f357bb7","tid":1679538,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T09:37:32.000Z","msg":"記得hocc之前有個特輯係訪問香港既indie band<br />\n我覺得佢可以用翻同樣既方法訪問唔同既抗爭者<br />\n香港， 甚至於加泰羅尼亞， 智利， 印尼 等等<br />\n<br />\n雖然呢d野外國不嬲都做緊"},{"pid":"ce2469c234de0dc61fb0c94a19ce07dfb4a80c19","tid":1679538,"uid":35190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T11:02:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}